parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank Cracking behind Front Right Mounting Bolt
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the fuel tank can cause fuel to leak, which can lead to a fire hazard, especially since the fuel is routed to drip near the exhaust pipes.
symptoms: residue or leaks around the fuel tank
visible cracks in the weld along the right side of the gas tank.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Poor Service and Response from Suzuki and Dealerships
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of acknowledgement and remedy from Suzuki and dealerships can lead to frustration and safety risks for owners, as they may not receive proper repairs or replacements.
symptoms: lack of clear instructions or solutions.
